steps.name: Given I am on the HOME page
When I clock in the timesheet with PIN "8573"
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('8', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('5', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('7', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('3', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title') }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'CONFIRM', exact: true })
Then I should see the employee "Evelyn" in the employee list
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
And I should see the "Manicure" service
When I add the "Manicure" service to my cart
And I add the "Pedicure" service to my cart
Then I should see my cart showing 2 item added
When I click on the total price of "Manicure"
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__menu li').getByText('CHANGE PRICE', { exact: true }).first()
Click locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__menu li').getByText('CHANGE PRICE', { exact: true }).first()
When I click on the "Pay" button
And I select the "Credit" payment type
And I fill the last 4 digits of card number "1234"
And I select the "VISA" on the menu
Then I should see the payment history "VISA (1234)$25.75" visible
When I click on the "Close Ticket" button
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Close Ticket', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Close Ticket', exact: true })
Then I should see the selected "SERVICE" tab on the Home page
When I select the "CLOSED TICKET" tab
Then I should see the toast message "Ticket data refreshed successfully" visible
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('.MuiAlert-message').filter({ hasText: 'Ticket data refreshed successfully' })
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I wait for the page fully loaded
When I reopen ticket with payment amount "$25.75"
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
And I should see the user info "Evelyn" in the ticket
When I select the service "Manicure" in my cart
And I select the "VOID ITEM" on the menu
And I select the reason "Wrong Item"
Then I should not see the service "Manicure" in my cart
And I should see my cart showing 1 item added
When I click on the "Pay" button
Then I should see the payment history "VISA (1234)$25.75" visible
When I select the payment history "VISA (1234)$25.75"
And I click on the "VOID" button
